high_descs: Walk into the living room and go to the sofa.
Pick up the pan from the sofa with the egg on it.
Walk to the fridge and stop in front of it.
Put the pan in the fridge, open the fridge and get the pan out of it.
Take the pan to the countertop.
Put the pan next to the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Moving the pan from the living room to the countertop in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn left, leave the small room, then continue straight out of the hallway all the way near the opposite wall, then right beside the table and get to the middle of the sofa.
Pick up a pan from the sofa.
Move back around the table the same way you went there, but this time head straight to the kitchen counter and then right to the fridge.
Put the pan inside the fridge, leave it for a bit to cool, then take it out.
Turn left so you can see the countertop.
Put the pan on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Cool the pan in the fridge and place it on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn left and head down the room and walk to the sofa on the right.
Pick up the pan in the middle of the sofa.
Head right to reach the fridge.
Cool the pan in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to reach the counter top.
Put the pan on the counter  top.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pan on the counter  top.
